      <div class="specs-section">
        <h3>Safety and Security</h3>
        <ul class="specs-list">
          <li><span>Toyota Safety Sense (TSS)</span><span>With</span></li>
          <li><span>SRS Airbags</span><span>Driver, Passenger, Side, Curtain Shield</span></li>
          <li><span>Anti-Lock Brake System (ABS)</span><span>With Brake Assist</span></li>
          <li><span>Vehicle Stability Control (VSC)</span><span>With</span></li>
          <li><span>Hill-Start Assist Control (HAC)</span><span>With</span></li>
          <li><span>Child Restraint System</span><span>With ISOFIX: 2</span></li>
